Watch the Activate Singapore TV ad which has been appearing on Channel News Asia in advance of the event on 16 and 17 January.Activate is the Guardian's platform for leaders working across a range of sectors who are using the internet to change the world. In partnership with the global consultancy MediaGuru, and working with the likes of the United Nations, Omidyar Network, the Nanyang Technological University, Ernst & Young and UK Trade & Investment, The Guardian will bring Activate to South East Asia for the first time. For more on Activate Singapore and to register click this link. 